START
ask user for what type of math they want to do
store users input
ask the user for first number
store the first number
ask the user for second number
store the second number
if users input is +
    add first and second number
    store as number three
    output number three
if users input is -
    subtract the first number from the second number
    store as number three
    output number three
if users input is *
    multiply number one by number two
    store as number three
    output number three
if users input is /
    divide number one by number two
    store as number three
    output number three
if users input is !
    close program
else
    output error incorrect input
repeat from step 2 until user enters !
END
